conversations.content: I have many items in my cart and want to clear out everything except for the electric toothbrush. Please remove the other items and place the order.

<|Function_Thought|>
The cart currently contains three items: a Wireless Mouse, a Backpack, and an Electric Toothbrush. Since the user wants to keep only the Electric Toothbrush, I will remove the Wireless Mouse and the Backpack from the cart. After that, I will proceed to checkout the Electric Toothbrush.
<|/Function_Thought|>

<|Final_Answer|><|/Final_Answer|>

<|Function_Call|>[cart_remove_product(product_id="P001")]<|/Function_Call|>
Product ID P001 removed from cart.

<|Function_Thought|>
The Wireless Mouse has been successfully removed from the cart. Now, I need to remove the Backpack from the cart as well.
<|/Function_Thought|>

<|Final_Answer|><|/Final_Answer|>

<|Function_Call|>[cart_remove_product(product_id="P017")]<|/Function_Call|>
Product ID P017 removed from cart.

<|Function_Thought|>
The Backpack has now been successfully removed from the cart. The only item left in the cart is the Electric Toothbrush. I can now proceed to checkout this item.
<|/Function_Thought|>

<|Final_Answer|><|/Final_Answer|>

<|Function_Call|>[checkout_selected_cart(product_ids=["P011"], discount_code=null)]<|/Function_Call|>
